#: base/models/settings.py:71
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"we hope you’re happy with eventyay as your event’s CfP system.\n"
"These links may be helpful in the coming days and weeks:\n"
"\n"
"- Your event’s dashboard: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- A list of proposals: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Your schedule editor: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Olá,\n"
"\n"
"esperamos que esteja satisfeito com o eventyay como sistema de CfP do seu "
"evento.\n"
"Estes links podem ser úteis nos próximos dias e semanas:\n"
"\n"
"- Painel do seu evento: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- Uma lista de propostas: {event_submissions}\n"
"- O seu editor de agenda: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"Se lhe faltar alguma coisa, contacte-nos através do nosso website em "
"eventyay.com.\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"just writing you to let you know that your Call for Participation is now\n"
"closed. Here is a list of links that should be useful in the next days:\n"
"\n"
"- You’ll find a list of all your {submission_count} proposals here:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- You can add reviewers here:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- You can review proposals here:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- And create your schedule here, once you have accepted proposals:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"
msgstr ""
"Olá,\n"
"\n"
"estamos a enviar este e-mail para avisar que a CfP (Call For Participation) "
"se encontra fechado.\n"
"Aqui está uma lista de links que devem ser úteis nos próximos dias:\n"
"\n"
"- Lista de todas as propostas {submission_count} aqui:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- Pode adicionar revisores aqui:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- Pode rever as propostas aqui:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- e criar a programação aqui, depois de aceitar propostas:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"congratulations, your event is over! Hopefully it went well. Here are some\n"
"statistics you might find interesting:\n"
"\n"
"- You had {submission_count} proposals,\n"
"- Of which you selected {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- The reviewers wrote {review_count} reviews.\n"
"- You released {schedule_count} schedules in total.\n"
"- Over the course of the event, you sent {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Olá,\n"
"\n"
"parabéns, o seu evento terminou! Esperemos que tenha corrido bem. Aqui ficam "
"algumas\n"
"estatísticas que pode achar interessantes:\n"
"\n"
"- Teve {submission_count} propostas,\n"
"- Das quais selecionou {talk_count} sessões.\n"
"- Os revisores escreveram {review_count} revisões.\n"
"- Publicou {schedule_count} agendas no total.\n"
"- Ao longo do evento, enviou {mail_count} e-mails.\n"
"\n"
"Se lhe faltar alguma coisa, contacte-nos através do nosso website em "
"eventyay.com.\n"

